{"type":"message","id":"b26c9db9","parentId":"fbc16e8b","timestamp":"2026-03-02T08:16:24.071Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3a9c9e7e91474bbcb627ea41","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The inventory refers to the inventory tab google sheet: 1RobrLNYSmMUyq53dUcdmj2ePaU2YkagqLqgIgx7M4OU\nThe cleaning refers to the cleaning tab of google sheet: 1RobrLNYSmMUyq53dUcdmj2ePaU2YkagqLqgIgx7M4OU\nThe lease command ALSO uses the same Google Sheet ID: 1RobrLNYSmMUyq53dUcdmj2ePaU2YkagqLqgIgx7M4OU (Inventory, Cleaning, Rent Tracker, and Inventory Data tabs are all inside this sheet.)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772439384064}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d25b9b2","parentId":"b26c9db9","timestamp":"2026-03-02T08:16:32.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so:\n- No daily memory files exist yet (fresh setup)\n- MEMORY.md exists and has some basic info about Google Sheets\n- IDENTITY.md is completely blank\n- USER.md is completely blank\n- SOUL.md is the standard template\n\nThis is definitely a first-run situation. According to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should introduce myself and ask who I am.\n\nBut the user asked me to greet them in my configured persona. Since there IS no configured persona yet, I should be direct and ask for help figuring it out.\n\nLet me be straightforward about this - no fluff, just the facts.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online and... I don't actually know who I am yet. My identity files are blank. Want to help me figure that out — name, vibe, what kind of creature I am?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":325,"output":295,"cacheRead":14848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15468,"cost":{"input":0.0001235,"output":0.0005015,"cacheRead":0.0028211200000000003,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034461200000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772439384072}}
