{"type":"message","id":"4959bc61","parentId":"476f0fe6","timestamp":"2026-03-02T08:43:53.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the Cleaning sheet, Row 2 (index 1):\n- Who: \"Vinny\"\n- Contacts: \"khizerahmad711@gmail.com\"\n- Building: \"90 Washington Apt 24M\"\n- Room 1 Tenant: \"Zayan Yaseen\"\n- Room 1 Contact: \"  1,234,567,890 \" (placeholder)\n- Room 2 Tenant: \"Zayan\"\n- Room 2 Contact: \"\"\n- Room 3 Tenant: \"Amir Shayganmehr\"\n- Room 3 Contact: \" 929-500-5162 \"\n\nI notice that Room 1's contact is still showing \"1,234,567,890\" which is a placeholder. The user wants to update it to \"1234567890\" (no commas, no leading 1). Actually wait, looking at the user's input: \"contact is 1234567890\" - they said \"1234567890\", not \"1,234,567,890\".\n\nActually, I'm not sure if \"1,234,567,890\" is meant to be a placeholder or the actual phone number. Let me look more carefully. The user said \"contact is 1234567890\" - this is 10 digits. \"1,234,567,890\" would be formatted as 1234567890. So they might be the same number, just formatted differently.\n\nLet me now create a manual update using the batchWrite command to update:\n1. The Cleaning sheet to update Room 1's contact\n2. Maybe check if the Rent Tracker needs updating\n\nBut actually, let me re-examine the user's request. They said:\n\"lease apartment 90 Washington 24M room 1 to zayan from 11/11/2026 to 12/12/2026. Zayan email is zayanyaseen99@gmail.com and contact is 1234567890.\"\n\nLooking at the current data:\n\n\n- Inventory sheet already has \"Zayan Yaseen\" for Room 1 with availability starting \"11-Nov\" ✓\n- Rent Tracker already has \"Zayan Yaseen\" with email and phone ✓\n- Cleaning sheet has \"Zayan Yaseen\" but contact might need updating ✓\n\nI'll carefully verify the phone number format. The cleaning sheet shows \"1,234,567,890\" which appears to be a placeholder, not the actual contact information. The contact definitely needs to be updated to \"1234567890\".","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I can see the data is already mostly in place! Looking at the sheets:\n\n**Inventory Sheet:** Zayan Yaseen is already listed for 90 Washington Room 1 with availability starting 11-Nov ✓\n\n**Rent Tracker:** Zayan Yaseen is already there with email and phone ✓\n\n**Cleaning Sheet:** Zayan Yaseen is listed, but the contact shows \"1,234,567,890\" which looks like a placeholder. Let me update it to the correct contact \"1234567890\":"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1bd16a6c4a5145bdbd8daa95","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd \"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\google-sheets-api\"; node scripts/sheets-cli.js write 1RobrLNYSmMUyq53dUcdmj2ePaU2YkagqLqgIgx7M4OU \"Cleaning!AE2\" '\"1234567890\"'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1890,"output":1300,"cacheRead":26220,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29410,"cost":{"input":0.0007182,"output":0.00221,"cacheRead":0.0049818,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00791}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772440960677}}
